feat(hy3): dump_tree dispatcher -- active workspace tree as JSON

Adds hl.plugin.hy3.dump_tree("<path>")() which writes the active
workspace's hy3 node tree to <path> as JSON. Window nodes carry the
Hyprland address (matches hyprctl clients .address); group nodes carry
their layout (root/splith/splitv/tabs) + children. Lets a consumer tell
loose windows at root from a root tab group without guessing geometry.
Delivered via a file because hyprctl eval only returns "ok".
